import random

def row_strategy(history):
    # Always open with 0
    if not history:
        return 0
    
    # Analyze the last move
    last_their_move = history[-1][1]
    
    # With 80% probability, the opponent will repeat our last move
    # If they picked the same as us last time, repeat it to get mutual payoff
    if last_their_move == history[-1][0]:
        return history[-1][0]
    
    # If they didn't follow, switch to the other strategy
    return 1 if history[-1][0] == 0 else 0
